{"tid":328530,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"小白鼠求收養","createTime":"2017-07-19T15:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T01:02:57.000Z","uid":128779,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5fb2cd342f6d2e0b505f2bd4ba397b93ed4838b6","tid":328530,"uid":128779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:53:12.000Z","msg":"同女友係某爬蟲店見到d喂蛇用bb鼠 未開眼好得意 諗到佢地一生出黎就要比人食覺得好慘 咁就試驗性質咁買左兩隻番去試下養唔養得大(預左死）<br />\n去左蘿蔔寵物店到買bb及孕鼠用奶粉人手用針筒餵<br />\n結果成功養到開眼同識食固體食物飲水 <br />\n但屋企已經太多寵物冇位養 加上家母開始有少少怨言 所以希望有人收養"},{"pid":"5aa68ba7160c0f04acdf61aa7ba1ed200f561b73","tid":328530,"uid":1436,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:54:57.000Z","msg":"賣俾啲有養蛇既巴打"},{"pid":"f7d9e0ff8d247f38555c1aabd936bf5efb35532a","tid":328530,"uid":128779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/235456_59e359c612a8a1b889de01b017afd238.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F235456_59e359c612a8a1b889de01b017afd238.jpg&h=3c94c66d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/235457_7c8f00c5daceb88c3784c4d8b2a02c51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F235457_7c8f00c5daceb88c3784c4d8b2a02c51.jpg&h=fc6ddf56&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/235458_1056dd9c7a5c31764738f1c6d5bf9355.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F235458_1056dd9c7a5c31764738f1c6d5bf9355.jpg&h=22622868&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/235458_c8538375030c6abda96d51d12bc48836.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F235458_c8538375030c6abda96d51d12bc48836.jpg&h=8ebe8648&s={SIZE}\" />