收番人錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n車錢我都未同你計呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收錢目的係唔想比人拎去餵蛇姐 <br />\n你係有心養我到貼車錢送比你又點話</blockquote><br />\n完全唔明收錢點解就唔可以餵蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當買糧</blockquote><br />\n出面我收既價錢可以買到8，9隻<br />\n我諗應該唔會有人用呢個價買兩隻呱"},{"pid":"fcf8b51f9b0e70c7215bb063cbaa4c9f72cc86cc","tid":328530,"uid":44031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:24:10.000Z","msg":"小白同大白品種唔同 小白好惡 <br />\n喂唔飽會有同類互食<br />\n好難訓練 巴打們3思"},{"pid":"10d718f39029612f4fc9486529a2a6ff11a3a9df","tid":328530,"uid":128953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:24:25.000Z","msg":"想搵水魚收養你隻白老鼠? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8773e1a412c7280f82c0991a262f16678e962e13","tid":328530,"uid":128779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:24:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白老鼠就白老鼠喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有兩種 有大白小白"},{"pid":"2db267861adae5dbc19b937516c0a0b6124cc0c7","tid":328530,"uid":65931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:45:42.000Z","msg":"比蛇食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed99fec8250496ba2a6b161dedb2810b9a212e25","tid":328530,"uid":90820,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"其實救得幾多隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間舖賣咗原本拎嚟餵蛇嘅老鼠仔畀你<br />\n佢就唔會再用其他老鼠仔餵蛇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好明白見到動物好無助/需要幫助/就死嗰時<br />\n真係會有惻隱之心去救佢哋<br />\n但有心救就要對佢哋負責到底<br />\n<br />\n我有養龜<br />\n見到金魚街/公園啲池入面嘅棄龜生活環境好差<br />\n但我可以做啲乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算隻隻買晒返嚟我都養唔起佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你既然係同女朋友一齊救老鼠仔<br />\n咁女朋友屋企又可唔可以養佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好救完之後自我感覺良好<br />\n然後就將隻老鼠仔掉上連登<br />\n你哋選擇咗負起呢個責任<br />\n就要一揹揹到底"},{"pid":"94f25260ee643c52b4a757522e235495565430c8","tid":328530,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:21:57.000Z","msg":"我都有呢個籠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0627294205c79e895600742d98c2202470284781","tid":328530,"uid":65591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:59:24.000Z","msg":"好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">不過唔養得</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"33708d04f342cdde35497126214b1f67ecc6a2bd","tid":328530,"uid":22349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:51:45.000Z","msg":"貪得意買玩厭就唔養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1981f19a0c9d4f52cdc471dbd08171d815bd23c3","tid":328530,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:52:14.000Z","msg":"$70 賣白老鼠？"}]}